# CRITICAL: Password/secret/key patterns (SPECIFIC to avoid blocking UI components)
**/*[Pp]assword*.txt
**/*[Pp]assword*.env
**/*[Pp]assword*.json
**/*[Pp]assword*.yml
**/*[Pp]assword*.yaml
**/*[Pp]assword*.config
**/*[Pp]assword*.xml
**/*[Pp]assword*.ini
**/*[Pp]assword*.properties
**/*[Ss]ecret*.txt
**/*[Ss]ecret*.env
**/*[Ss]ecret*.json
**/*[Ss]ecret*.yml
**/*[Ss]ecret*.yaml
**/*[Ss]ecret*.config
**/*[Kk]ey*.txt
# PGP public key is safe to commit (not a secret)
!**/public/.well-known/pgp-key.txt
**/*[Kk]ey*.env
**/*[Kk]ey*.json
**/*[Kk]ey*.yml
**/*[Kk]ey*.yaml
**/*[Kk]ey*.config
**/*actual[_-]password*
**/*real[_-]secret*
**/*private[_-]key*

